---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me — hkg">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">About Me</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Welcome to my page. My name is Haroon but sometimes people call me hkg or just H.
        If you found your way here, chances are, you were handed an inconspicuous business
        card with a url and trusted it enough to punch it into your search engine of choice.
      </p>
      <p>
        This website is made to be a creative outlet etc etc but really I just saw someone
        else's website and thought it was super cool, so I copied the entire thing. And made
        it pink of course.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've included some inspiration, advice, and knowledge that I have collected over the
        years, as well as just some things I'm passionate about.
      </p>
      <p>
        I like trying new things, meeting interesting people, and questioning everything ever
        in life. I also like normal guy stuff like cars, the gym, guns, music, and video games.
        I think it's worth mentioning that I have an incredibly optimistic outlook on life and
        everyone around me.{" "}
        <a
          href="/history"
          class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors"
        >click here for the history of me.</a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>
